        <h1>Google Ads Management for Small Businesses</h1>
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span>By <strong>Freeland Marketing &amp; Entertainment</strong></span>
          <span>Palm Coast, FL</span>
          <span>Serving All of Florida</span>
        </div>
